    <div class="px-8 py-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About Baldrick</h2>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
            Baldrick is more than just a name - it's a philosophy. We believe that the best technology should be as cunning as a fox who's just been appointed Professor of Cunning at Oxford University.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-4 mb-8">
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
