                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-3">
                <p class="text-sm text-yellow-700">
                  <strong>Our Mission:</strong> To create controller boards that are not just functional, but delightfully clever and surprisingly powerful.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- The Name Section -->
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">The Name</h3>
          
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            The name "Baldrick" comes from the cunning character in the classic British comedy "Blackadder." Just like our namesake, our boards are designed to be clever, resourceful, and surprisingly effective despite their humble appearance.
          </p>

          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            When you choose a Baldrick board, you're not just getting a controller - you're getting a piece of technology that thinks outside the box, finds clever solutions to complex problems, and does it all with a touch of British wit.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">What Makes Baldrick Special</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• <strong>Clever Design:</strong> Every board is designed with intelligence and efficiency in mind</li>
              <li>• <strong>British Engineering:</strong> Built with the precision and reliability you'd expect from British craftsmanship</li>
              <li>• <strong>Community Focus:</strong> Created by enthusiasts, for enthusiasts</li>
              <li>• <strong>Innovation:</strong> Constantly pushing the boundaries of what's possible in lighting control</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- The Boards Section -->
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Boards</h3>
          
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            From pixel controllers to relay boards, from interactive controllers to power distribution units, every Baldrick board is designed with the same philosophy: make it simple, make it clever, make it work.
          </p>

          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Whether you're building a small display or a massive installation, there's a Baldrick board that's perfect for your needs. And thanks to our innovative Turnip Network, they all work together seamlessly.
          </p>

          <!-- Call to Action -->
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Ready to Get Started?</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Explore our range of boards and discover how Baldrick can bring your lighting projects to life.
            </p>
            <a href="/boards" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
              View All Boards
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Learn More Section -->
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Learn More</h3>
          
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Want to dive deeper into the Baldrick ecosystem? Check out our <a href="/breakthroughs" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Baldrick Breakthroughs</a> section to learn about our innovative technologies like the Turnip Network, Kluster, and more.
          </p>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <a href="/breakthroughs" class="block bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Baldrick Breakthroughs</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Discover our innovative technologies and ecosystem</p>
            </a>
            
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
